er\" title=\"Orton Merryweather\">Orton Merryweather</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25%;\">\n<p><b>Mentioned:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Willas_Tyrell\" title=\"Willas Tyrell\">Willas Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ilyn_Payne\" title=\"Ilyn Payne\">Ilyn Payne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lancel_Lannister\" title=\"Lancel Lannister\">Lancel Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tanda_Stokeworth\" title=\"Tanda Stokeworth\">Tanda Stokeworth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Garth_Tyrell\" title=\"Garth Tyrell\">Garth Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Leonette_Fossoway\" title=\"Leonette Fossoway\">Leonette Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tysha\" title=\"Tysha\">Tysha</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mordane\" title=\"Mordane\">Mordane</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mentions\">Mentions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_28&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Mentions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:20%;\">\n<p><b>Houses:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/